00:17:23.270 --> 00:17:24.349
I can wait for you.

00:17:26.829 --> 00:17:28.270
Let alone a few days,

00:17:29.170 --> 00:17:30.570
even if it takes years,

00:17:31.590 --> 00:17:32.550
