After getting to know him,

00:27:00.040 --> 00:27:02.860
my view of the Jade Linglong
has completely changed.

00:27:02.860 --> 00:27:05.240
Besides, the Jade Linglong has chosen him.

00:27:05.240 --> 00:27:07.270
